header.gameNote: SPORTSTIME OHIO BCA CLASSIC AT COLUMBUS OH

article.headline: Virginia Military 104, South Dakota State 89
article.story: COLUMBUS, Ohio (AP) -- Reggie Williams scored a career-high 36 points and grabbed 11 rebounds Sunday to lead VMI to a 104-89 win over South Dakota State, placing seventh in the BCA Classic at Ohio State's Value City Arena. VMI (1-2) shot 46 percent from the field in the first half to build a 58-42 lead. South Dakota State (0-3) scored six points to open the second half, cutting VMI's lead to 10, but the Keydets answered with an 8-0 run. Fred Robinson had 24 points, Travis Holmes had 16 and Matt Murrer added 10 for the Keydets. Andy Kleinjan led South Dakota State with 23 points. Cam Hornby scored 20, Kai Williams had 17 and Blake Yackley added 13 for the Jackrabbits, who shot 48 percent from the field and had 33 turnovers.
